title: Poetry - Supposed To Be Byron
description:
For some strange reason this has a load of other stuff that was not written by Lord Byron.   Walt Whitman, T.S Eliot...and others.
   They were in there when I got this.   So I&#039;ve just left it as it was.
You know that theory...?   The one about if you let monkeys loose on a typewriter then eventually the monkeys will manage to produce the entire works of Shakespeare.   Well this monkey has just been let loose.   And I&#039;m upping this and not The Bard.   
   Must dash.   There&#039;s a little orangutan that looks a bit hot.
